## Quality Checklist

- [ ] Stats are sourced (company name, survey name, or "industry analyst estimates")
- [ ] Disruption levels are justified (High = fundamental role change, Moderate = augmentation)
- [ ] Capabilities framework covers all 9 operational motions
- [ ] Key insights are specific to the target company, not generic
- [ ] Roles listed are actual job titles used at the target company or industry
- [ ] Maturity levels reflect actual market readiness (not aspirational)
